headline: PRINGLES速 IS BRINGING BOLD NEW FLAVORS TO THE SNACK AISLE WITH SIX SMOKY, SALTY AND SWEET INNOVATIONS
summary: When it comes to Pringles速, flavor innovation never takes a summer vacation. The brand is continuing to deliver what its fans crave with more new, unique flavor combinations hitting shelves starting in September. From a brand-new collection of crisps with a smoky twist to launching a well-known flavor combination and introducing new sweet and savory Pringles Mingles flavors, there is truly something to satisfy every craving.
